>\n1. 警方違法向多名記者開槍，棍打記者<br />\n2. 警方違法瞄準市民頭部發射布袋彈和橡膠子彈<br />\n3. 在沒有任何襲擊下，警方違法向婦孺、伯伯開槍<br />\n4. 警方違法向市民投擲鐵枝、磗頭<br />\n5. 隻字不提一些市民向警方掟水樽垃圾等之前，警方在多處在沒有受到任何襲擊，提出任何警告下，違法突然向市民開槍，不斷發射催淚彈，布袋彈和橡膠子彈，導致局勢快速失控<br />\n6.隻字不提有市民於6月15日於太古廣場因展示示威標語墮樓, 送院搶救後不治的事實<br />\n<br />\n投訴表格：<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=xNvf4PJMmDX7L7bksShbPj11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=bd00b814\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日期： 2019/6/12 時間1830 新聞報導</span></span>"},{"pid":"e16e7037049e05bb69eb19a1f385e1bdc2588199","tid":1232483,"uid":179409,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:57:57.000Z","msg":"開晒馬路行都迫到爆呀天才<br />\n平時住港島嘅人會唔會行埋馬路呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e34a1d595673755de009ad955f3301498e868c6","tid":1232483,"uid":80396,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:58:46.000Z","msg":"所以凌晨條街冇人，等於成個港島零人口？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f9fd6e88f089a0512a154223c452e701521ef1","tid":1232483,"uid":10157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:01:49.000Z","msg":"假膠煩唔撚煩，呢d時候黎消費<br />\n樓主老母比狗屌完生出黎係唔同d<br />\n見一個block一個"},{"pid":"ff44d6525b8403dee393bc9afdee6cb6a566575b","tid":1232483,"uid":26656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:06:05.000Z","msg":"香港咁細點解會容納到700萬人 可唔可以唔好再落黎同快啲返上去大陸呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1332988e8d3692f5617cbd102d33a8f266072cb2","tid":1232483,"uid":53815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T1